# In Progress — {{PROJECT_NAME}}

> The live **in-progress board** (🔄). **The planner** (sole writer of `planning/*.md`) **moves a task here** from `todo.md` at dispatch,
> and **out** to `memory/completed-tasks.md` on merge — workers never edit this file. Each entry names its **owner** so
> concurrent sessions never collide and a resumed session knows which task is its own. Dates absolute.
> *(Where-are-we = this board + the top of `memory/completed-tasks.md`; what's-next = `todo.md`.)*
>
> **Owner format** — `owner: <handle> · session: <uuid>`: `<handle>` = the stable worker name, `<session>` =
> its live `$CLAUDE_CODE_SESSION_ID` (echo it, never guess) — the exact key the resume hook matches when a session resumes.

